data.description: Come take look at this stunning three bedroom, two bathroom home. This spacious home features a big carport with generous storage space and a large lot. Inside, you'll find plenty of room for your family to spread out and relax. The bedrooms are generously sized, and the two bathrooms provide convenience and privacy. The kitchen is perfect for entertaining with its ample counter space. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful house your new home!
